{"word":"G3679 - ὀνειδίζω - oneidízō - on-i-did'-zo - Cast in teeth","slug":"G3679","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀνειδίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>oneidízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>on-i-did'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cast in teeth"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BF;&#x0313;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x03B4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - oneidezo&#x0304;</b> - <i>on-i-did'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3681\">G3681</a>; to <i>defame</i>, that is, <i>rail at</i>, <i>chide</i>, <i>taunt:</i> - cast in teeth, (suffer) reproach, revile, upbraid."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3680\">G3680</a>, <a href=\"#/G3681\">G3681</a>"}]}